# ATLAS State Management Directory

This directory contains NgRx state management for ATLAS features.

State slices to be implemented:
- deployments/ - Deployment state (actions, reducers, effects, selectors)
- ai-analysis/ - AI analysis state
- approvals/ - Approval state
- exceptions/ - Exception state
- agents/ - Agent state
- query-builder/ - Query builder state

Each state slice follows the pattern:
- {feature}.actions.ts - Action definitions
- {feature}.reducer.ts - Pure state transitions
- {feature}.effects.ts - Side effects (API calls)
- {feature}.selectors.ts - Memoized state selectors
- {feature}.state.ts - State interface definition
